title: I always did like Twisted Fate.
body:
https://i.gyazo.com/73d81867efc1fc16f9a739dca359c237.png

He doesn't have the lane-winning power of 90% of the roster, but that's because he has so much universal pressure. 

I don't play him a lot, but I do like him. Maybe this will make me start playing him.
